Gui

Class FileParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • Gui.FileParser

  • public class FileParser
extends java.lang.Object
    A file parser that will take in a file of raw comma separated values (csv) and create a map that maps their value to their index location. e.g. 1,2,4,17,91,34,1337,... -> [ [0, 1], [1, 2], [2, 4], [3, 17], ...] This is used to quickly generate the list of indices in which the target value exists and facilitates the creation of the Oracle for Grover's Algorithm.
    Author:
    William Hunter McNichols
